Where do you start a journey into community-led change?

Here! With Launch, a short online course for new & emerging groups wanting to reimagine/rebuild their world.

Introducing the Transition approach, tips & tools to help you start on firm foundations.

The two-part workshop will run on 18 November and 2 December online, find out more and sign up here: https://transitiontogether.org.uk/training/

content:
New rear light arrived, it worrrkkkkssss woohoo! I just tested it through the whole coil of cable from which I will cut some, when wiring it up properly - so not attached it or the cable to the bike yet.

Will be happy to have a new functioning rear light though :)

What I did only just realise though is that there was no mention of + or - which first surprised me, then I was like oh, of course the dynamo puts out AC. Nice. Which is why these LED bike lights flicker at slow speeds, presumably.

The article questions whether advanced artificial intelligence can do a better job at identifying life-like characteristics.
